data.description:
www.1122RipplingSprings.com - Gorgeous DR Horton home has Entry w/hand scraped wood floors that extend into Den, Formal Dining & Study. Den with high ceilings and an abundance of natural lighting. Kitchen with a wealth of cabinetry & counter space. Oversized Master Suite with new carpet & dedicated a/c unit. Fabulous Master Bathroom with oversized, tiled shower with inlay; dual, granite vanities, framed mirrors, wood-look tile & generous walk-in closet. All secondary bedrooms w/walk-in closets. Covered patio & playset!

Please visit my MLS Site Search.RealtyByMonica.com for more current listings or my buyer's website BuyRealEstateWithMonica.com for Buyer info and testimonials. Check out my fan page - RealtyByMonicaFanPage.com for the latest news.
